comments: LeVert (IND) brings his hand forward towards Graham's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Washington Jr. (IND) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to New Orleans.
LeVert (IND) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps after his gather.
Valanciunas (NOP) and Craig (IND) briefly engage and disengage as they reach for the rebound.
Craig (IND) and Alexander-Walker (NOP) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they are falling out of bounds.
As Hart (NOP) reaches for the rebound, marginal contact occurs with Craig (IND).
Alexander-Walker (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Indiana.
Jones (NOP) deflects the ball with his hand prior to his foot making any contact with the ball.
Jones (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Indiana.
Washington Jr. (IND) moves somewhat laterally towards Alexander-Walker's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Duarte (IND) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Brissett (IND) moves somewhat backwards towards Valanciunas (NOP) and marginal contact occurs as Valanciunas secures the ball.
Jones (NOP) and LeVert (IND) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as LeVert secures the ball.
Valanciunas (NOP) is already in Craig's (IND) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Brissett (IND) cleanly blocks Alexander-Walker's (NOP) shot near the rim.  The marginal body contact is caused as Alexander-Walker cuts back towards the rim.
Brissett (IND) and Hart (NOP) briefly engage and disengage as they reach for the rebound.
LeVert (IND) makes contact to Hart's (NOP) arm that affects his SQBR.
Jones (NOP) contests LeVert's (IND) jump shot and marginal contact occurs after the release.
Valanciunas (NOP) goes to not through LeVert's (IND) space during the inbound.
Brissett (IND) makes contact to Graham's (NOP) arm prior to making any contact with the ball.
Hart (NOP) extends his hand into Brissett's (IND) body and initiates contact during his jump shot attempt.
Craig (IND) attempts to tie up Hart (NOP) and does not maintain contact with the ball.
Brissett (IND) makes contact to Hart's (NOP) arm and body as he attempts to tie up Hart.
LeVert (IND) lifts and re-plants his pivot foot prior to releasing his shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) jumps to the side of LeVert (IND) and avoids making contact with LeVert as he contests the jump shot.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Alexander-Walker (NOP).
